The '''singing fig trees''' were a biological anomaly in [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] that were once found on [[Pil Diller]]. They became extinct sometime before the rise of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]], and were represented at the [[Holographic Zoo of Extinct Animals]].

